{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"10083-hugs-in-the-city","title":"Câlins dans la ville.","description":"Voici Jilly. Aujourd'hui, elle a câliné la plupart des chats de la ville !","language":"French","langCode":"fr","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Cyrille Largillier"],"illustrators":["JP Brouard","Kalynne Vorster"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/10083-hugs-in-the-city"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29567/size3/3b99c56a34d0cfcfc37440bdd0610dd7.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29567/size6/3b99c56a34d0cfcfc37440bdd0610dd7.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29704/size6/0143049e7e2d83b1ecf5e3295e87dd01.jpg","text":"Je m'appelle Jilly.\nAujourd'hui, j'ai câliné\nla plupart des chats\nde la ville !","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29570/size6/9718063c5f55d085e9a5221913814082.jpg","text":"J'ai câliné Ben, le chat des voisins.\nMiaou ?\nBen dit : « Miaou ? »","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29573/size6/615037a38d80c4d3201d8f1c2d5f24ad.jpg","text":"J'ai câliné le chat qui vit\nsous le banc dans le parc.\nIl ondula\net se tortilla.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29574/size6/05584af56f8c06d4d1b81850f4c27869.jpg","text":"J'ai câliné le chat roux\net dodu de Mme Lilly.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29575/size6/ea5b90609a687a12b38282a66aa2a261.jpg","text":"Il m'a léché le visage.\n« Slurp, slurp, slurp. »\nSLURP !","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29578/size6/4aeb4fc3879487db16df2609f049a47d.jpg","text":"J'ai câliné le chat qui mange à l'extérieur\ndu restaurant de poisson-frites.\nIl est venu : « miam miam. »","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29582/size6/45bc58a13c2f2aad40040dc0b98246c2.jpg","text":"J'ai même câliné le chat grincheux\nqui n'aime pas les câlins.\nIl grogna et grogna.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29587/size6/8a68e302dc5258a97361f6349abfb1a0.jpg","text":"J'ai câliné un chat long.\nJ'ai câliné un chat court.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29585/size6/75e2a894ca2cdc815d490e8fad8cd1e3.jpg","text":"J'ai câliné un vieux chat.\nJ'ai câliné un jeune chat.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29586/size6/71b9ddab843d828c0f8e3684c2e26428.jpg","text":"J'ai câliné une maman - chatte.\nEt tous ses petits chatons.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29588/size6/b90bf9999b741814ac8b58271718cbb2.jpg","text":"J'ai essayé de câliner les gros chats\ndu zoo mais le gardien a dit :\n« NON ! »","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29589/size6/caa32c191ef19676e3cede3ad3ab596d.jpg","text":"J'ai grimpé dans un bus et j'ai câliné le chat \nqui était caché dans le sac d'une vieille dame.\nLa vieille dame hurla !\nHURLA !","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29591/size6/b4c3c1ee8099be513fd607a8419d4cd4.jpg","text":"Je suis rentrée à la maison et suis allée me coucher.\nOAAAHHHH !\nQuelques machins à fourrure\nse sont glissés dans mon lit...","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29592/size6/d2e1f7905eaf67d9bba3c46945aec282.jpg","text":"et me câlinent.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/29593/size6/d4abf83fdbd4cb0ce6bb1b81d44c76aa.jpg","text":"16/16","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":15,"words":207}}